HEADWORD: Intentness
<hw>In*tent"ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state or quality of being
intent; close application; attention.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Extreme solicitude or <qex>intentness</qex> upon business.</q>
<rj><qau>South.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

